metadata.name: The Mimographer (unmasked-ish)
metadata.description:
There's been a lot of talk around town regarding who is the creator behind Theatre Paumé and The Mimes of New York. It's time you all know the true identity of the Mime behind the Mimes.  
While some of you may already be acquainted with me, there are undoubtedly those who remain unfamiliar. My name is Omar Z. Robles, and it is my honor to introduce Theatre Paumé—a visionary realm I have meticulously crafted as an experimental haven for the exploration of innovative concepts, employing unconventional channels such as artificial intelligence.

I extend my sincere gratitude to each and every one of you for accompanying me on this captivating journey thus far, and I eagerly anticipate the continued sharing of further experiments with all of you.
